data.description: Welcome to this great remodeled home with the possibility of an ADU. Property features include recessed lighting, beautiful waterproof laminate and tiled flooring. The 2 separate kitchens have new cabinets, granite counter tops, and new appliances. The bathrooms have new lighting, vanities and tiled showers. It also has a fresh interior and exterior coat of paint. The lot is over 9,000 sqft, boasting a detached 2 car garage with additional parking space for an RV or any recreational toys you may have. This is an incredible find and can be perfect for an extended family that wants to live together.
